units si
boundary p p p
atom_style full
neighbor 2.0e-11 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check no exclude type 1 3
read_data data.si
timestep 5e-16
fix 1 all nve
pair_style deepmd lrmodel.pb
pair_coeff * *

bond_style zero
bond_coeff *
special_bonds lj/coul 1 1 1 angle no
kspace_style pppm/dplr 1e-5
kspace_modify gewald 4e9 diff ik mesh 10 10 10
fix 0 all dplr model lrmodel.pb type_associate 1 3 bond_type 1

dump 1 all custom 1 01.xyz id type x y z fx fy fz
dump_modify 1 sort id

run 1
